{"tid":2139352,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝕讓成交】內地客2160萬沽柏蔚山3房  帳面貶值701萬","createTime":"2020-08-04T08:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T16:50:07.000Z","uid":248578,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"997e51d2d4a3b463b71e88f376786cf803911cbf","tid":2139352,"uid":248578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:32:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2714736/%E3%80%90%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E3%80%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A22160%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E6%9F%8F%E8%94%9A%E5%B1%B13%E6%88%BF%20%C2%A0%E5%B8%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC701%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2714736%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A22160%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E6%259F%258F%25E8%2594%259A%25E5%25B1%25B13%25E6%2588%25BF%2520%25C2%25A0%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E5%2580%25BC701%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=2df3ee04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2714736/%E3%80%90%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E3%80%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A22160%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E6%9F%8F%E8%94%9A%E5%B1%B13%E6%88%BF%20%C2%A0%E5%B8%B3%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC701%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，北角柏蔚山3座低層G室，實用面積911平方呎，屬於3房連工人房間隔，座向北面，望園景，屬銀主盤，以2,300萬元成交，呎價25,247元，低市價逾1成。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主為許姓內地生，多年前大舉在香港掃貨，包括北角柏傲山、何文田天鑄、南昌站匯璽等等，最終財困大幅蝕讓散貨。上述單位2018年6月購入，當時作價2,861萬元，其後淪為銀主盤，持貨約2年，帳面貶值701萬元離場。"},{"pid":"abd2ba7b3bdedc7ebb4e57784b305433080993b0","tid":2139352,"uid":72173,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"分分又係D掛高500萬再掛正常又話咩忍痛離場"},{"pid":"7f94633f096780357e49b2ea6cccaadd17c1ee37","tid":2139352,"uid":138197,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"abd2ba7b3bdedc7ebb4e57784b305433080993